.*A*                                                                           
PASFMT is a Pascal "pretty-print" program that is invoked as
 
    !PASFMT.X source_fid TO|ON|OVER newsource_fid
 
There are options (such as indenting level) inside the program
that can only be changed by a recompile of PASFMT.
.*K* XINDEX
